---
title: HelloHero: Italian Plant-Based Mince Pasta with Baby Leaves & Cheddar Cheese
description: Pasta with a cheesy tomato sauce, veggies and the combo of plant-based, all packed into one amazing piled-high pasta. If that’s what you were hoping for, then this dish won’t disappoint you!
